    "description": "游戏介绍<br>你发现自己被锁在自己的家中，发现了犯罪现场，除此之外你什么也记不得。在这个恐怖场景中，你会发现一位不速之客在房屋周围徘徊，这让你逃跑的可能性越来越渺茫。<br>解决所有的挑战和谜题，逃离周围的危险，弄清你家里发生的事情，并恢复你丢失的记忆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388110/extras/d3ef08c5e34f0ee444acec0465b0b810.poster.avif?t=1699502674\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388110/extras/d3ef08c5e34f0ee444acec0465b0b810.mp4?t=1699502674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《谋杀凶案》是一款指向点击游戏，你需要解决谜题，找出犯罪凶手。<br><br>- 神秘而不确定的故事：不速之客，失踪的记忆，还有需要解决的凶案。<br>- 引人入胜的视觉效果：水墨画风的图形创造了对比强烈和忧郁的气氛。<br>- 有趣的配乐：为给故事增添神秘和恐怖氛围而创作的配乐。<br>- 很多挑战：探索整个房屋，解决许多挑战，最终找出问题的答案<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388110/extras/28b9010f2345ec7f168f0c90341bca2e.poster.avif?t=1699502674\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388110/extras/28b9010f2345ec7f168f0c90341bca2e.webm?t=1699502674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388110/extras/28b9010f2345ec7f168f0c90341bca2e.mp4?t=1699502674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
